Oomnitza,is,an,IT,asset,management,service,that,allows,users,to,manage,assets,in,the,cloud,and,access,information,on,those,assets,from,any,mobile,device,or,web,browser,Oomnitza,users,can,perform,an,inventory,of,all,their,IT,assets,modify,existing,assets,track,assets,across,multiple,users,and,locations,push,updates,and,create,service,requests,Oomnitza,comes,with,an,advanced,permissions,system,to,control,access,to,important,data,and,functions